2.6 The COMMON-EXTENSIONS module

found?

Function

Summary

Returns true if object is not equal to $unfound, and false otherwise.

Signature

found? object => boolean

Arguments

object
An instance of <object>.

Values

boolean
An instance of <boolean>.

Library

common-extensions

Module

common-extensions

Description

Returns true if object is not equal to $unfound, and false otherwise.

It uses \= as the equivalence predicate.
